data.description:
Welcome to this Chic 1 Bed, 1 Bath Luxury Condo in the Heart of the Central West End. This stylish home boasts luxury vinyl floors, a trendy 3D square wall design, stainless appliances, spacious bedroom & closet. Seamlessly blending functional design with modern aesthetics. Walls are freshly painted by a licensed company, and the chic furnishings are negotiable.

Glamour and easy access to the dynamic spirit of St. Louis. Immerse yourself in the history of the city and local attractions, fine dining, boutique shopping all at your doorstep. Building features:24 hour Doorman, Gated Parking avail thru HOA for additional monthly fee and 5G Ready. Heated pool, AC and Heat included in HOA. Stunning view of the iconic St. Louis Arch from your terrace, and swim in the secluded pool. With its unique features, trendy design elements, and prime location, this condo offers an unparalleled living experience in a Vibrant Urban Setting!!!
